longBusinessSummary: IntroMedic Co., Ltd. develops and supplies medical equipment in South Korea and internationally. It offers MiroCam, a capsule endoscope system; E.G. Scan, a disposable ductile esophagoscope; and EndoClot, an absorbent hemostasis equipment. IntroMedic Co., Ltd. was formerly known as Metis Medical Systems Co., Ltd. and changed its name to IntroMedic Co., Ltd. in March 2006. The company was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Seoul, South Korea.
